@page "/"
@*<h1 class="text-left">About Expense Tracker</h1>*@
<div class="card">
    <img src=@bannerImageLocation class="card-img-top" alt="Monthly Expenses Tracker" height="200">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">About Expense Tracker</h5>
        <p class="card-text">
            Expense Tracker is a single page web application. Which helps to track and manage daily basis expenses.
            This application gives simple chart to visualize the expense on various parameters such as expense category, Currency, Payment type and methods and more..
            <br />
            The Expense Tracker also gives the flexibility to upload bank / credit card statement as monthly expenses.
            Those expenses can be categories  using inbuilt rules. These rule are customizable too.
            <br />
            End of the month it helps you to do quick analysis of your expense as well.
            Also, It has expense history to track your expenses in past.
            <br />

            <br />

        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
            <b>Technical Features</b><br />
            Expense Tracker is Experimental Service side Blazor application. Hosted on Azure as App
            Service using consumption plan.
            <br />
            This Application is designed & developed using Sqlite Database, Interfacing with
            Entity Framework using Repository pattern.

            <br /> - Bootstrap used for CSS based design.
            <br /> - Modal Dialog form has been implemented for Add, Update and Delete
            <br /> - Reuse of Modal Dialog for various operations
            <br /> - Bulk Insert made possible to import expenses from 3rd party statements
            <br /> - Expense category, payment types will be auto detected using customizable rules
            <br /> - Chart.Js used to populate various types of charts 

            <br />... Design & Development is on going (more will be coming soon..)
        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
            <small class="text-muted">

                Last updated on: <b>@lastUpdate</b><br />
                Source Code can be found <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/DeepakkSHAW/ExpenseTracker.Server"> @@github</a>
            </small>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<p class="text-justify">

</p>





